libdxfrw

libdxfrw is a free C++ library to read and write DXF files in both formats, ascii and binary form.
It also has DWG read/write support in LibreCAD's in-tree fork. See
DWG_REFERENCE_COVERAGE_STATUS.md and DWG_ROADMAP.md for current DWG coverage
notes.
It is licensed under the terms of the GNU General Public License version 2 (or at your option
any later version).


If you are looking for historical information about the project, check:
http://sourceforge.net/projects/libdxfrw

== Building and installing the library ==

Use the typical
./configure
make
make install (as root)

For LibreCAD's in-tree fork, the top-level LibreCAD CMake build is the primary
tested build definition.

== Example usage of the library ==

See LibreCAD's DXF/DWG filter integration in librecad/src/lib/filters/.
